01:32:37,932 --> 01:32:41,227
Cell phone PIN code:
1954

779
01:33:24,270 --> 01:33:26,690
Rose, it's Felix.

780
01:33:27,023 --> 01:33:28,733
One night, an airport,

781
01:33:29,067 --> 01:33:33,154
a man, a woman.
No, I won't be a memory, Rose.

782
01:33:33,405 --> 01:33:34,823
Fuck logic.

783
01:33:35,073 --> 01:33:38,785
So life isn't a Hollywood movie
with a happy end.

784
01:33:39,035 --> 01:33:42,330
So what if I keep
switching languages!

785
01:33:42,997 --> 01:33:46,001
We have to invent our own happy end.

786
01:33:46,251 --> 01:33:48,920
Anyway, as someone said,

787
01:33:49,379 --> 01:33:51,840
it all depends
on when you stop the movie.

788
01:33:52,090 --> 01:33:55,176
Well, let's stop
the movie now, Rose.

789
01:33:57,929 --> 01:34:02,058
Wherever you are,
whether it's night or day,

790
01:34:02,308 --> 01:34:03,727
there must be palm trees,

791
01:34:03,977 --> 01:34:07,689
music, the sea and all that jazz.

792
01:34:08,648 --> 01:34:11,985
but I'm waiting here.
I forgot...

793
01:34:12,235 --> 01:34:14,362
I'm in Burgundy, at my father's.

794
01:34:14,612 --> 01:34:18,116
It's a house I'm sure you'll like.

795
01:34:21,828 --> 01:34:23,955
Catch the next plane.

796
01:34:24,205 --> 01:34:27,500
I'll be at the airport.
The place grew on me.

797
01:34:27,751 --> 01:34:31,880
I'll get a room at the Hilton
and wait for every flight.

798
01:34:32,756 --> 01:34:34,174
Fuck fine cuisine.

799
01:34:35,258 --> 01:34:36,760
Oh, I almost forgot:

800
01:34:37,552 --> 01:34:39,596
I'm totally in love with you.

801
01:34:39,846 --> 01:34:43,975
I won't promise anything...
I mean, I promise you everything.

802
01:34:44,225 --> 01:34:47,520
You can reach me at 04 60 01 50 10.

803
01:34:47,771 --> 01:34:48,646
This is Felix.

804
01:34:48,813 --> 01:34:50,648
Call me.

805
01:35:20,011 --> 01:35:23,932
Please, sir,
back to the airport.

806
01:35:24,182 --> 01:35:26,226
The airport, please.
